      p Copyrights &copy; PMdev 2024
    small
      p Profanity The REST API is free and will be, but these services cost real $$$ to maintain, so I will be happy to be sponsored if you can patronize my site. Thank you, feel like you created it too!
      .link-box
        a(class="btn icons" href="https://github.com/Malzagic/wulgaryzmy-api" target="_blank")
          i.fab.fa-github
          span github
        a(class="btn icons" href="https://paypal.me/pmloczkowski?country.x=PL&locale.x=pl_PL" target="_blank")
          i.fab.fa-cc-paypal
